item.title: 关于测序数据质控
item.description: 关于测序数据质控 学习资料收集 1.3质控结果解读 质控软件fastqc官网FastQC aims to provide a simple way to do some quality control checks on raw sequence data coming from high throughput sequencing pipelines. It provides a modular set of analyses which you can use to give a quick impression of whether your data has any problems of which you should be aware before doing any further analysis.
